  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Decision record records Accepted based on aggregate engineering judgment; however, the structured factor evidence contains at least one achievedLevel strictly below requiredLevel, constituting a rebutting defeater (W-AR-02).",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-req",
